author_ssm: Colin Torre, 2012. Media updates by Rhyannon J. Rodriguez.
abstract_ssm: This collection contains the original artwork, photocopies, and audio and video recordings produced by the Good Girl and Win street art projects as conceived and executed by artist Pam Butler in Buffalo and New York during the 1990s.
